1. Introduction¶

Suicide is a major public health problem and a leading cause of death in the world. According to the description Wikipedia, suicides resulted in 828,000 deaths worldwide in 2015 and now is the 10th leading cause of death. This is a frustrating fact that so many people decide to end their life. Today we want to do some analysis on the dataset Suicide Rates Overview 1985 to 2016 from Kaggle refers United Nations Development Program, World Health Organization. Following the final tutorial, we will collect, process, visualize the data. Our goal is to find the specific people at a higher suicide risk than other. We hope the public can do more to reduce the suicide rate.

df8=df.groupby(["sex","country"]).sum()
df8=df8.reset_index()
df9=df.groupby("country").sum()
df9=df9.reset_index()
female_percent=[]
total_percent=[]
for index, row in df9.iterrows():
    total_suicides=df9['suicides_no'][index]
    country=df9['country'][index]
    temp=(df8.loc[(df8['country'] == country) &(df8['sex'] == "female")])
    if(total_suicides==0):
        female_rate=0
    else:
        female_rate=temp.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
    
    female_percent.append(female_rate)
    total_percent.append(100)
df9["female_percent"]=female_percent
df9["total_percent"]=total_percent

df10=df.groupby(["age","country"]).sum()
df10=df10.reset_index()
age5to14_p=[]
age15to24_p=[]
age25to34_p=[]
age35to54_p=[]
age55to74_p=[]
#age75_p=[]
for index, row in df9.iterrows():
    total_suicides=df9['suicides_no'][index]
    country=df9['country'][index]
    age5to14_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "5-14 years")])
    age15to24_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "15-24 years")])
    age25to34_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "25-34 years")])
    age35to54_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "35-54 years")])
    age55to74_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "55-74 years")])
    if(total_suicides==0):
        age5to14_rate=0
        age15to24_rate=0
        age25to34_rate=0
        age35to54_rate=0
        age55to74_rate=0
    else:
        if(age5to14_num.empty==False):
            age5to14_rate=age5to14_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
        else:
            age5to14_rate=0
        age15to24_rate=age15to24_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
        age25to34_rate=age25to34_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
        age35to54_rate=age35to54_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
        age55to74_rate=age55to74_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/total_suicides*100
    
    age5to14_p.append(age5to14_rate)
    age15to24_p.append(age15to24_rate)
    age25to34_p.append(age25to34_rate)
    age35to54_p.append(age35to54_rate)
    age55to74_p.append(age55to74_rate)
    

df9["age5to14_p"]=age5to14_p
df9["age15to24_p"]=age15to24_p
df9["age25to34_p"]=age25to34_p
df9["age35to54_p"]=age35to54_p
df9["age55to74_p"]=age55to74_p

In [167]:
df10=df.groupby(["age","country"]).sum()
df10=df10.reset_index()
df9=df.groupby("country").sum()
df9=df9.reset_index()

age5to14_p=[]
age15to24_p=[]
age25to34_p=[]
age35to54_p=[]
age55to74_p=[]
age75_p=[]

for index, row in df9.iterrows():
    total_suicides=df9['suicides_no'][index]
    country=df9['country'][index]
    age5to14_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "5-14 years")])
    age15to24_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "15-24 years")])
    age25to34_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "25-34 years")])
    age35to54_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "35-54 years")])
    age55to74_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "55-74 years")])
    age75_num=(df10.loc[(df10['country'] == country) &(df10['age'] == "75+ years")])

    if(total_suicides==0):
        age5to14_rate=0
        age15to24_rate=0
        age25to34_rate=0
        age35to54_rate=0
        age55to74_rate=0
        age75_rate=0
    else:
        if(age5to14_num.empty==False):
            age5to14_rate=age5to14_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age5to14_num.iloc[0]['population']
        else:
            age5to14_rate=0
        if(age15to24_num.empty==False):
            age15to24_rate=age15to24_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age15to24_num.iloc[0]['population']
        else:
            age15to24_rate=0
            
        age25to34_rate=age25to34_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age25to34_num.iloc[0]['population']
        age35to54_rate=age35to54_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age35to54_num.iloc[0]['population']
        age55to74_rate=age55to74_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age55to74_num.iloc[0]['population']
        age75_rate=age75_num.iloc[0]['suicides_no']/age75_num.iloc[0]['population']
        
    total=age5to14_rate+age15to24_rate+age25to34_rate+age35to54_rate+age55to74_rate+age75_rate
    if total!=0:
        age5to14_p.append(age5to14_rate/total*100)
        age15to24_p.append(age15to24_rate/total*100)
        age25to34_p.append(age25to34_rate/total*100)
        age35to54_p.append(age35to54_rate/total*100)
        age55to74_p.append(age55to74_rate/total*100)
    else:
        age5to14_p.append(0)
        age15to24_p.append(0)
        age25to34_p.append(0)
        age35to54_p.append(0)
        age55to74_p.append(0)
